Package: lockbox
Type: Package
Title: Simple File Encryption and Secrets Management in R
Description: Simple file encryption and secrets management for R using modern cryptographic tools. Provides functions to encrypt/decrypt files with 'age' and manage secrets in encrypted YAML files with 'SOPS'. Secrets can be easily exported as environment variables for use with APIs and services. Supports both file-based and in-memory key management workflows.
Version: 0.0.1
URL: https://vincentarelbundock.github.io/lockbox
BugReports: https://github.com/vincentarelbundock/lockbox/issues
Authors@R: c(
